that had the sort of texture...

57:12.611 --> 57:14.545
of what American life
is like now.

57:14.547 --> 57:16.914
- This tsunami of stuff just comin' at you.
- Right.

57:16.916 --> 57:20.151
Also, it's not unfun, I don't think.
No. I don't think so either.

57:20.153 --> 57:23.354
No. Not at all. I mean, although it
