59:10.761 --> 59:13.596
If something sells really well,
gets a lot of attention,

59:13.598 --> 59:15.799
it's gotta be shit, right?
Right. Of course.

59:15.800 --> 59:18.066
The ultimate irony is, if your
thing starts selling well,

59:18.068 --> 59:19.601
